"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-05-15-paris-olympics-ticket-app-resale-platform-goes-live\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS,\\u00a0France\\u00a0(AFP) - The official 2024 Paris Olympics app went live on Wednesday, enabling ticket holders to obtain their places and resell seats for any unwanted sessions, the organising committee announced.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9831930087366385, \"rank\": 0.00765890630119941, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The application \\\"paris2024tickets\\\" is the \\\"only official and authorised resale channel: the resale is completely transparent for both the seller and the purchaser,\\\" the organising committee said in a statement.\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most events for the July 26-August 11 Games have quickly sold out during multiple ticket releases since last year, with around 8.27 million places purchased in total.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There remain tickets for the Olympic football, however, while most sports are still available for the Paralympics which take place from August 28-September 8.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The app will be \\\"the essential tool for accessing your tickets for the Olympic Games Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On competition day, only a ticket presented on the Paris 2024 tickets app will allow access to the venues,\\\" the organising committee said.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999965627921, \"rank\": 3.437164559620741e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It enables buyers to transfer tickets to their fellow travellers and will be used to obtain the QR codes that must be shown to security at venues.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The QR codes \\\"are not visible for the moment to prevent counterfeiting,\\\" Michael Aloisio, director general of the Paris organising committee, told reporters.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999960855907818, \"rank\": 3.9144245822313965e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES  Comments are closed.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": []}]}"